6. UAN Adventure: The Digital Identity Game

Target stakeholders: Members, young employees, HR staff
Game format: Web-based adventure puzzle

The player’s UAN is the central identity. They must complete tasks to unlock EPFO services.

Tasks include:

Activate UAN
Link Aadhaar
Update bank account
Add nominee
Transfer previous PF
Download passbook
File claim
Track grievance

Learning outcomes:

Members learn step-by-step digital EPFO services.

Example levels:

Level 1: UAN Activation
Level 2: KYC Dungeon
Level 3: Nomination Castle
Level 4: Transfer Bridge
Level 5: Claim Portal
Level 6: Pension Gate

Gamification:

Digital readiness score, “KYC Master” badge, “Nomination Completed” badge, “Transfer Champion” badge.
